    - Closed CompactionPolicy enum: Auto / OperatorApproval (default per §11.5) / Disabled. Serde wire tokens lowercase.
    - CompactionWorker struct with sync tick(&mut self, backend, now) primitive — production wraps in tokio::time::interval task (documented; not shipped per spec carry-forward).
    - approve_segment(&SegmentId) records out-of-band operator authorisation. Segments approved before becoming eligible are parked and consumed on the tick when eligibility kicks in.
    - CompactionReport carries eligible_segments / compacted_segments / awaiting_approval / receipts_removed / index_entries_pruned. Serializable for §20 telemetry.
    - CompactionBackend trait: list_sealed_segments / compact_segment / emit_approval_required. Both InMemoryEvidenceLog and RocksDbEvidenceLog implement it.
